e France-Presse]] |date= 21 October 2014 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20141211151545/http://www.afp.com/en/node/2965382/ |archivedate= 2014年12月11日 |accessdate= 2015年1月25日 }}<br>[http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/11/27/us-ukraine-crisis-parliament-idUSKCN0JB1IQ20141127 War veterans steal limelight in Ukraine's new parliament] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/11/27/us-ukraine-crisis-parliament-idUSKCN0JB1IQ20141127 |date=20151007021510 }}, [[路透社|路透社]] (27 November 2014)</ref>

