===第聂伯营===
{{main|{{link-en|第聂伯营|Dnipro Battalion}}}}
也称作第聂伯-1营（Dnepr-1）。在[[顿巴斯战争|顿巴斯战争]]最初阶段，[[乌克兰陆军|乌克兰政府军]]{{tsl|en|25th Airborne Brigade (Ukraine)|第25空降旅}}在[[斯拉维扬斯克|斯拉维扬斯克]]与亲俄武装交战中放弃装备，乘公交车撤逃回[[第聂伯罗彼得罗夫斯克|第聂伯罗彼得罗夫斯克]]，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://un.ua/eng/article/504866.html|title=Turchynov Tells Defence Ministry Disestablish 25th Brigade Of Air Assault Forces|work=Ukrainian News|date=April 17, 2014|access-date=2015-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417223308/http://un.ua/eng/article/504866.html|archive-date=2014-04-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>新当选的州长[[伊戈尔·科洛莫伊斯基|伊戈尔·科洛莫伊斯基]]与第聂伯罗彼得罗夫斯克市长{{tsl|en|Ivan Kulichenko|伊万·库利琴科}}担心这座居民大部分说俄语的城市失陷，于2014年4月迅速组建了极右民族主义志愿者组成的第聂伯营。该营从{{tsl|en|Ukrainian oligarchs|乌克兰寡头}}[[伊戈尔·科洛莫伊斯基|伊戈尔·科洛莫伊斯基]]获得了大量捐赠。因此绰号“科洛莫伊斯基的营”。<ref name=WSJ2714>[http://online.wsj.com/articles/ukraines-secret-weapon-feisty-oligarch-ihor-kolomoisky-1403886665 Ukraine's Secret Weapon: Feisty Oligarch Ihor Kolomoisky] {{Wayback|url=http://online.wsj.com/articles/ukraines-secret-weapon-feisty-oligarch-ihor-kolomoisky-1403886665 |date=20201214015056 }}, [[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]] (June 27, 2014)</ref>据估计科洛莫伊斯基州长个人资助第聂伯营超过1000万美元。<ref name="enjoys strong support from the local population">[http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/06/12/dnipropetrovsk-the-ukrainian-town-determined-to-stop-putin.html The Town Determined to Stop Putin] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/06/12/dnipropetrovsk-the-ukrainian-town-determined-to-stop-putin.html |date=20170504161028 }}, [[The_Daily_Beast|The Daily Beast]] (12 June 2014)</ref>第聂伯营作为全乌克兰首批组建的地方作战营，是积极对[[顿涅茨克人民共和国|顿涅茨克人民共和国]]作战的主力。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/06/12/dnipropetrovsk-the-ukrainian-town-determined-to-stop-putin.html|title=The Town Determined to Stop Putin|work=The Daily Beast|date=June 12, 2014|accessdate=2015-01-25|archive-date=2017-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170504161028/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/06/12/dnipropetrovsk-the-ukrainian-town-determined-to-stop-putin.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年8月27日，由于东乌克兰战局急转直下，基辅爆发大规模游行示威，抗议者聚集在总统波罗申科办公室门口，要求政府援救被东部亲俄武装围困在乌俄边境的伊兹伐里内小镇达15天之久的四个志愿者战斗营：“顿巴斯”营、“米洛特沃涅茨”营、“赫尔松”营、“第聂伯-1”营。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20140828/41764122_0.shtml#p=1 |title=乌克兰四个精锐营被围15天 亲属在首都集体哭讼 |accessdate=2015-01-25 |archive-date=2017-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170105104055/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20140828/41764122_0.shtml#p=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年10月9日，第聂伯营在[[台尔曼诺沃|台尔曼诺沃]]交战中，宣称击毙了若干名车臣人，包括其领袖Andrei Borisov；以及3名俄军人，分别是俄罗斯将军Sergey Andreychenko、士兵Vladimir Lysyakov 和Vasiliy Protasov。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://euromaidanpress.com/2014/10/14/ukrainian-battalion-says-russian-general-killed-in-operation-in-donetsk/|publisher=Euromaidan Press|title=Ukrainian battalion says Russian general killed in operation in Donetsk|accessdate=2015-01-25|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125031940/http://euromaidanpress.com/2014/10/14/ukrainian-battalion-says-russian-general-killed-in-operation-in-donetsk/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年10月31日“[[顿涅茨克人民共和国|顿涅茨克人民共和国]]”总理[[亚历山大·扎哈尔琴科|亚历山大·扎哈尔琴科]]指控‘第聂伯-1’营曾驻扎的[[紅軍城_(烏克蘭)|红军城]]（[[顿涅茨克市|顿涅茨克市]]西北大约45公里）近400名年轻妇女失踪。 <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://world.people.com.cn/n/2014/1102/c1002-25957440.html |title=顿涅茨克称乌克兰红军城发现286具女尸 |accessdate=2015-01-25 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304092511/http://world.people.com.cn/n/2014/1102/c1002-25957440.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年底，第聂伯营首领{{tsl|en|Yuriy Bereza|尤里·别廖扎}}当选为国会议员。

===顿巴斯营===
{{main|顿巴斯营}}
[[File:Battalion_Donbass_Semenchenko2.jpg|thumb]]。|替代=]]
顿巴斯营是2014年乌克兰内战中最著名也是最早的地方作战营。被乌克兰媒体称为“小黑人”以类比于克里木危机中的[[小绿人_(格鲁乌)|小绿人]]。顿巴斯营由俄裔乌克兰籍的{{tsl|en|Semen Semenchenko|谢苗·谢缅琴科}}创建并领导。其成员是反对东乌克兰分离的俄语居民志愿者。这类似于反对车臣独立的由[[车臣人|车臣人]]组成的拥护莫斯科中央政府的东方营（Vostok Battalion）。

顿巴斯营组建后其成员变得多样性，包括了来自全乌克兰的志愿者与外国人。顿巴斯营人数超过了1000，积极参加了[[顿巴斯战争|顿巴斯战争]]的主要战斗。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://iwpr.net/report-news/volunteers-bolster-ukraines-fighting-force|title=Volunteers Bolster Ukraine's Fighting Force|work=Institute for War and Peace Reporting|last=Shynkarenko|first=Oleg|date=June 26, 2014|accessdate=2015-01-25|archive-date=2014-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015065442/http://iwpr.net/report-news/volunteers-bolster-ukraines-fighting-force|dead-url=no}}</ref>还参加了2014年8月底的保卫[[马里乌波尔|马里乌波尔]]的战斗。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/donbas-battalion-sends-groups-of-tank-destroyers-to-stop-armored-vehicles-that-crossed-into-ukraine-near-novoazovsk-361956.html|title=Donbas battalion sends groups of tank destroyers to stop armored vehicles that crossed into Ukraine near Novoazovsk|publisher=Kyiv Post|date=25 Aug 2014|accessdate=2015-01-25|archive-date=2014-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140825201625/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/donbas-battalion-sends-groups-of-tank-destroyers-to-stop-armored-vehicles-that-crossed-into-ukraine-near-novoazovsk-361956.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2014年8月底亲俄武装的大反攻中，顿巴斯营遭受了严重损失。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://rt.com/news/182404-donetsk-forces-trap-hardware/|title=Anti-govt forces ‘circle 1000s of Kiev troops, capture 2 tank battalions’ in E.Ukraine|publisher=RT|date=25 Aug 2014|accessdate=2015-01-25|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126131709/https://www.rt.com/news/182404-donetsk-forces-trap-hardware/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年9月，顿巴斯营重建。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.liga.net/news/politics/3180498-batalon_donbass_preobrazovan_v_batalonno_takticheskuyu_gruppu.htm|title=Батальон "Донбасс" преобразован в батальонно-тактическую группу|publisher=Liga|accessdate=2015-01-25|archive-date=2017-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170715204333/http://news.liga.net/news/politics/3180498-batalon_donbass_preobrazovan_v_batalonno_takticheskuyu_gruppu.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>并列为[[乌克兰民族卫队|乌克兰民族卫队]]第3后备营。 

